FROM python:3.10-slim as base-image

FROM python:3.10-slim as runtime-image
WORKDIR /service
COPY --from=base-image /service/.venv ./.venv
ENTRYPOINT ["/service/.venv/bin/python3", "-m", "feedforbot"]
